{{ 'aaw-customer-voices.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

<section class="aaw-voices aaw-voices--{{ section.settings.layout_mode }}" aria-labelledby="aaw-voices-title-{{ section.id }}">
  <div class="aaw-voices__wrap">
    <div class="aaw-voices__head">
      <div>
        <p class="aaw-voices__kicker">{{ section.settings.eyebrow }}</p>
        <h2 id="aaw-voices-title-{{ section.id }}">{{ section.settings.heading }}</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="aaw-voices__intro">
        <p>{{ section.settings.intro }}</p>
        {% if section.settings.layout_mode == 'home' %}
          <a class="aaw-voices__link" href="{{ section.settings.page_link }}">Read more customer voices</a>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>

    {% if section.settings.layout_mode == 'page' %}
      <div class="aaw-voices__hero">
        <figure>
          <img src="{{ 'aaw-ins-gallery-custom-2025.webp' | asset_url }}" alt="AAW custom in-ear monitor shell craft and finishing" width="900" height="900" loading="eager">
        </figure>
        <div>
          <span>Customer voices</span>
          <h3>Real owner impressions from AAW listeners around the world.</h3>
          <p>Collected through AAW dealers via Judge.me, these comments focus on fit, sound, comfort, and everyday listening.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="aaw-voices__grid">
      <article class="aaw-voice-card is-featured">
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote>I was very pleasantly surprised just how good AAW monitors are. The overall sound is quite balanced, they do have very detailed bass, sub bass and treble, but the mids are not so recessed as would be the case with more typical V shaped sounding IEM&#x27;s.</blockquote>
        <footer>Steve S.</footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card">
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote>Excellent product. This is my first CIEM and I can say I am very much impressed. It fits perfectly snugged in my ears. I thought it sounded just the same when using tunes on my phone, but when I plugged it in the monitors, I can hear clearly the distinct sounds. The vocals and the bass is clear and crisp.</blockquote>
        <footer>AJ L.</footer>
      </article>

      <article class="aaw-voice-card">
        <div class="aaw-voice-card__meta"><b>5 / 5</b></div>
        <blockquote>Great fit, great isolation, great material and good sound for the price. Sound wise is big and quite wide. Bass is satisfying and mids are ok just that the treble is very recessed but its what makes it non-fatiguing for long term listening. Overall an enjoyable iem.</blockquote>
        <footer>Elias T.</footer>
